{"sn11.15:0.1":"Samyutta Nikaya 11.15 ","sn11.15:0.2":"2. Dutiyavagga ","sn11.15:0.3":"Ramaneyyakasutta ","sn11.15:1.1":"Savatthiyam jetavane. ","sn11.15:1.2":"Atha kho sakko devanamindo yena bhagava tenupasankami; upasankamitva bhagavantam abhivadetva ekamantam atthasi. Ekamantam thito kho sakko devanamindo bhagavantam etadavoca: ","sn11.15:1.3":"“kim nu kho, bhante, bhumiramaneyyakan”ti? ","sn11.15:2.1":"“Aramacetya vanacetya, ","sn11.15:2.2":"pokkharanno sunimmita; ","sn11.15:2.3":"Manussaramaneyyassa, ","sn11.15:2.4":"kalam nagghanti solasim. ","sn11.15:3.1":"Game va yadi varanne, ","sn11.15:3.2":"Ninne va yadi va thale; ","sn11.15:3.3":"Yattha arahanto viharanti, ","sn11.15:3.4":"Tam bhumiramaneyyakan”ti. "}